### Component: LLM Provider Manager & SSSR On-Demand Loading

#### [MODIFY] [llm-provider-manager.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/src/core/operator/llm-provider-manager.ts)
- Add a helper `isOllamaModelHot(modelName: string): Promise<boolean>` to query Ollama's REST endpoint `/api/ps` for loaded models.
- If Ollama has the target model hot, route requests directly to Ollama with `keep_alive: -1` to prevent automatic unloading.
- In `generate`, implement **Single-Slot Sequential Runner (SSSR) Auto-loading**:
  - If `catalog.activeProviderId === "llamacpp"` and `this.llamaSupervisor` is attached, check if the slot is empty or in error.
  - If the requested model is not currently "ready" in the supervisor slot, retrieve the model file path:
    `const modelPath = this.llamaSupervisor.getModelPath(catalog.activeModel);`
    If found, block and await on-demand load:
    `await this.llamaSupervisor.loadModel(modelPath, catalog.activeModel, { ctxSize: 2048 });`
  - Re-evaluate active port dynamically before routing the Open-AI compatible request. This allows complete sequential multiplexing of the Main LLM and the Guardian Agent on a single slot.

